.DT
delete_item
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
delete_item

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
delete_item -  This method deletes the state/location information of a specific quest item owned by a player.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int delete_item(mixed pl_name,
mixed item)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^pl_name%^RESET%^ -   player object or name
%^BOLD%^item%^RESET%^ -      item object or identifier
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/item_tracker.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method deletes the state/location information of a specific quest item
owned by a player.


If the item isn't actually owned by the player it returns 0
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_item_state()

.EP

